#xcommand TEMPLATE USING &lt;v1&gt;&gt;[, &lt;vN&gt;]=&gt; ;

   #pragma __cstream | cFun:= "FUNCTION __Inline("+ &lt;"v1"&gt;[, &lt;"vN")&gt;])", AP_RPuts( InlinePrg( %s, cFun) )

//----------------------------------------------------------------//

function InlinePRG( cText , cFun)

   local nStart, nEnd, cCode

   while ( nStart := At( "&lt;?prg", cText ) ) != 0
      nEnd  = At( "?&gt;", SubStr( cText, nStart + 5 ) )
      cCode = SubStr( cText, nStart + 5, nEnd - 1 )
      cText = SubStr( cText, 1, nStart - 1 ) + ExecInline( cCode, cFun ) + ;
              SubStr( cText, nStart + nEnd + 6 )
   end

return cText

